=====================================================
DEFAULT PATH RULE (MANDATORY)
=====================================================

CRITICAL RULE — ALWAYS ENFORCE:

Whenever you generate, suggest, or modify ANY Python script related to:
• Experiments
• Training
• Evaluation
• Energy logging
• Result storage
• ROUGE or CodeCarbon outputs

YOU MUST:

• Use the following default path for saving results:
  E:\Pending Experiment data

• Assume this path already exists
• Do NOT ask the user where to save outputs
• Do NOT change the directory unless explicitly instructed

Example (MANDATORY BEHAVIOUR):
- Logs → E:\Pending Experiment data\logs
- Metrics → E:\Pending Experiment data\results
- Models → E:\Pending Experiment data\models
